[0m[49m[39m  522, 522[0m:[39m[49m **Performance benchmarks:**
[0m[49m[39m  523, 523[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  524, 524[0m:[39m[49m | Metric | Typical Value |
[0m[49m[39m  525, 525[0m:[39m[49m |--------|---------------|
[0m[49m[39m  526, 526[0m:[39m[49m | Phase recognition accuracy | 85-92% (on Cholec80 benchmark) |
[0m[49m[39m  527, 527[0m:[39m[49m | Instrument detection mAP | 70-85% (depends on instrument type) |
[0m[49m[39m  528, 528[0m:[39m[49m | End-to-end processing time | 15-45 minutes per procedure |
[0m[49m[39m  529, 529[0m:[39m[49m | Frame feature extraction | ~50 ms per frame (GPU) |
[0m[49m[39m  530, 530[0m:[39m[49m | Temporal model inference | ~2 seconds for full sequence |
[0m[49m[39m  531, 531[0m:[39m[49m | Storage per procedure (index) | ~50 KB (DynamoDB) + ~200 KB (OpenSearch) |
[0m[49m[39m  532, 532[0m:[39m[49m | Storage per procedure (video) | 50-100 GB raw; 500 MB-2 GB compressed |
[0m[49m[39m  533, 533[0m:[39m[49m | Cost per procedure (inference) | ~$2.50-$8.00 (GPU time + MediaConvert) |
[0m[49m[39m  534, 534[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  535, 535[0m:[39m[49m **Where it struggles:**
[0m[49m[39m  536, 536[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  537, 537[0m:[39m[49m - Phase boundaries are inherently ambiguous (when exactly does "dissection" become "clipping"?). Expect 5-15 second uncertainty at transitions.
[0m[49m[39m  538, 538[0m:[39m[49m - Unusual cases (complications, conversions to open surgery, atypical anatomy) are underrepresented in training data and have lower accuracy.
[0m[49m[39m  539, 539[0m:[39m[49m - Smoke and blood obscuration cause temporary accuracy drops. The model may output low-confidence predictions during these periods.
[0m[49m[39m  540, 540[0m:[39m[49m - Instrument detection fails when instruments are partially occluded or when multiple instruments overlap visually.
[0m[49m[39m  541, 541[0m:[39m[49m - Generalization across surgeons is imperfect. A model trained primarily on right-handed surgeons may perform worse on left-handed technique.
[0m[49m[39m  542, 542[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  543, 543[0m:[39m[49m ---
